@node "WZInput" "WZInput"
 WZInput
 Return Result of last Message
 For stringresults use this a$=peek$(WZInput) or wzinputstr
@endnode

@node "WZPrint" "WZPrint"
 WZPrint

 Set Gadgetvalues
                         1                 2                      3
 String               String with &  z.b WZGadgetSet #stringgad1,&i$
 Slider                Level              Min                      Max
 Scroller               Top             Visible                  Total
 Listview             Selected          Visible                  var.List
 Date                   Day              Month                    Year
 Cycle                 Active            Labels
 ArgGadget              arg0              arg1                    arg2
 Gauge                  Current           Total

 WZPrint "slider1",20   or  WZPrint #slider1,20
@endnode

